text: Shira Elinav (; born 26 April 2000) is an Israeli footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Israel women's national team. ==Career== Elinav has been capped for the Israel national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Israeli women's footballers Category:Israel women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Jewish footballers Category:Israeli Jews
